# Title
Dockerfile (Node.js 22 LTS + TypeScript build)

# File
## Dockerfile
```dockerfile
FROM node:22

WORKDIR /app

COPY provider ./provider
COPY backend ./backend
COPY frontend ./frontend

WORKDIR /app/provider
RUN npm install && npm run build
WORKDIR /app/backend
RUN npm install && npm run build

EXPOSE 4000 5000
VOLUME ["/app/provider"]

CMD sh -c "node /app/provider/dist/server.js & node /app/backend/dist/server.js"
```
